{
  "stem": "13471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'll tell you that I was officer in charge of a fleet of file cabinets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I finally got myself shipped out but with great difficulty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I found out that if I was gonna do anything in this man's Navy, I would have to do it myself [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had me down in Norfolk following people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, the hell with that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I looked around, I found out where I ought to be, and I pulled a few strings and made some requests.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I got up to, to, to Washington.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was doing better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I got this-- in this dead end, you see, with a goddamn whole room full of file cabinets.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These Navy officers, full, full four-striped captain, come in to see me and say, what do you have about the, the, the German aircraft capability in Dakar, West Africa?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would say, sir, I've got a whole file drawer full of stuff.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let me have a precis of it by close of business today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, close of business today was a half hour away, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was [LAUGHS] no way I could do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I would stay there til 8:00 or 9:00--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At night.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought, well, this is for the birds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to be back in by 6:30 in the morning, you see?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I didn't see daylight except through the dirty windows of that goddamn munitions building for months on end.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I gotta get out of here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I, I went over to the [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "BUPERS, ?] Bureau of Naval Personnel, which ran the assignment of Naval officers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I found some junior officers over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
